traits.locale_text: "Похоже, все, что уцелели, теперь прячутся под нам — патрули давно не приводили пленных".

languages.text: "It seems everybody who survived is hiding down below — the patrols haven't delivered any new prisoners in a while."

languages.text: “看来，所有活下来的家伙都躲到下面去了，巡逻队已经很久都没送来过新的囚犯了。”
languages.original_text: "It seems everybody who survived is hiding down below — the patrols haven't delivered any new prisoners in a while."

traits.locale_text: “看来，所有活下来的家伙都躲到下面去了，巡逻队已经很久都没送来过新的囚犯了。”

languages.text: «Parece que todos los supervivientes se ocultan más abajo; hace mucho que las patrullas no traen prisioneros nuevos».
languages.original_text: "It seems everybody who survived is hiding down below — the patrols haven't delivered any new prisoners in a while."

traits.locale_text: «Parece que todos los supervivientes se ocultan más abajo; hace mucho que las patrullas no traen prisioneros nuevos».

languages.text: 「生存者は全員、ずっと下に身を隠している…そして警備が新たに囚人を連れてきたということも今のところはない」
languages.original_text: "It seems everybody who survived is hiding down below — the patrols haven't delivered any new prisoners in a while."

traits.locale_text: 「生存者は全員、ずっと下に身を隠している…そして警備が新たに囚人を連れてきたということも今のところはない」

languages.text: « Apparemment, tous les survivants se cachent en bas. Ça fait un moment que les patrouilles n'ont plus amené de nouveaux prisonniers. »
languages.original_text: "It seems everybody who survived is hiding down below — the patrols haven't delivered any new prisoners in a while."

traits.locale_text: « Apparemment, tous les survivants se cachent en bas. Ça fait un moment que les patrouilles n'ont plus amené de nouveaux prisonniers. »

languages.text: "Anscheinend verstecken sich sämtliche Überlebenden in der Tiefe – die Patrouillen haben schon länger keine neuen Gefangenen ehr mitgebracht."
languages.original_text: "It seems everybody who survived is hiding down below — the patrols haven't delivered any new prisoners in a while."

traits.locale_text: "Anscheinend verstecken sich sämtliche Überlebenden in der Tiefe – die Patrouillen haben schon länger keine neuen Gefangenen ehr mitgebracht."

languages.text: "Hayatta kalan herkes aşağıda saklanıyor gibi gözüküyor. Uzun zamandır devriyelerden hiç yeni mahkûm gelmedi."
